<body>
    <div class="container">
    <div class="full">
    <div class="card card-default card-body">
        <div class="main-title">
            <h3 class="card-title">One Line Installation </h3>
            <h3><a href="https://github.com/eddiejibson/chae-install"/><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a><a href="https://twitter.com/chaedotsh"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a><a href="https://paypal.me/eddiejibson/5"/><i class="fab fa-paypal"></i></a></h3>
        </div>
        <button class="collapsible">Information</button>
        
        <div class="info">
                <p>Understandably, setting up a server from scratch is a pain. install.chae.sh assists you with this. You can select the packages you wish to install along with a variety of other tasks and it will generate a one-line command to complete the task for you. It can also handle various other tasks such as adding the correct PPAs, updating the system and downloading backups. This project is open source and can be found on <a href="https://github.com/eddiejibson/chae-install">GitHub</a>. Please submit a pull request if you add anything, we'd like to implement it!</p>

        </div>
        <div class="margin">
            <input class="input form-large" id="installUrl" type="text" value="Select packages below to create the URL"
                readonly onfocus="this.select()">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="selection">
    <% if (typeof install == "object") { %>
    <% install.categories.forEach((category) => { %>
    <h3>
        <%= category.title %>
    </h3>
    <ul>
        <% category.packages.forEach((package) => { %>

        <li><label><input class="checkbox" name="<%= package %>" type="checkbox">
                <%= install.packages[package].name %></label></li>
        <% if (typeof install.packages[package].children == "object") { %>
        <ul class="children">
        <% Object.keys(install.packages[package].children).forEach((child) => { %>
        <li><label><input class="checkbox" id="child" data-parent="<%= package %>" name="<%= child %>" type="checkbox"> <%= install.packages[package].children[child].name %></label></li>
        <% }); %>
        </ul>

        <% } %>

        <% }); %>
    </ul>

    <% }); %>
    <% } %>
    <p>Was the package or task you wanted not listed? <a href="https://github.com/eddiejibson/chae-install/blob/master/install.json">Add it here</a>.</p>
    </div>
    
    </div>
    </div>
    
    

